    "faq_KCW3XB": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_j4hAeK": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I listen to Voxblock audiobooks?",
            "content": "<p>To listen to our stories, you'll need to purchase a <a href=\"/products/voxblock-player\" title=\"Voxblock Audiobook Player\">Voxblock audiobook player</a>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_weGGzx": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the player easy to set up?",
            "content": "<p>There is no set-up involved with our player. It is completely wifi-free and is ready to use straight out the box. Just press and hold the play button to switch the player on, pop in an audiobook and start listening.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_3VkjFk": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How loud is the Voxblock player?",
            "content": "<p>Although the player has a loud in-built speaker, as this product is designed for children there is a cap for safe listening. Alternatively, headphones can be used by plugging them into the player, or with an aux to aux cable the player can be plugged into an additional external speaker.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_3ipDYf": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is this a children's product?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, Voxblock was designed as simple, low-tech product to allow children to access audiobooks. Due to the player's simple-to-use design, many customers have discovered this player for their elderly parents.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_cAbGgi": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are physical audiobooks?",
            "content": "<p>We have created tactile, tangible audiobooks to make audio stories more accessible instead of being hidden behind screens and subscriptions. Our audiobooks are blocks designed to look like miniature versions of the printed book so they can be displayed on a bookshelf alongside the rest of your book collection. </p>"
          }
        },
        "item_pMWXXx": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will I lose my place in the story if I remove a block?",
            "content": "<p>No, you can swap over titles and the block will remember where you last listened.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_MX6c3h": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "When will you release more adult audiobook titles?",
            "content": "<p>We have no immediate plans to release more titles suitable for adults. You may also find some nostalgic titles within our children's collection which may be suitable, such as, A Bear Called Paddington, Enid Blyton and other children's classics.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
